# Google Calendar Integration (Optional)
# Only needed if you want Google Calendar events on your new tab page.
# Without these, the extension works normally — just without Calendar support.

# 1. Get a Google OAuth client ID (Chrome Extension type) from Google Cloud Console
#    https://console.cloud.google.com/ → APIs & Services → Credentials
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com

# 2. Your extension's public key (base64) — only needed for stable extension ID
#    Leave commented for local development
# GOOGLE_EXTENSION_KEY=your_base64_encoded_public_key_here
